worthy environment for the people, it is stated in the press release.\n\nChief Justice Rana further stated that the day may create energy and inspiration among all. He said that the judiciary was always effortful to ensure justice to all and implement the provision of the constitution.\n\n\u201cThe constitution was not a document to run the state mechanisms as it was a progressive document of peoples\u2019 lifestyle,\u201d CJ Rana said. All state organs, mechanisms and bodies should play effective roles to materialize the dream of prosperity, he viewed.\n\nAccording to CJ Rana, the constitution was not only the document of political change but also the document of state restructuring, governance system and change in social and political systems.\n\nHe has also recalled that the constitution has ensured a multi-party democratic political system, civil liberty, human rights, periodic election, press freedom, independent judiciary and rule of law.","title":"CJ Rana extends best wishes of Constitution Day - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/19/128612/","video":[]}
